node.text: YouTuber, Shamook did such an amazing job creating his own deepfake versions of popular characters from Star Wars spin-off, The Mandalorian that Lucasfilm gave him a job 🙌👏

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'News Study suggestsrecovered COVID patients may have significantly reduced intelligence'.

node.text: The research, conducted by Imperial College London adds to a growing list of concerns about the long-lasting impact of COVID-19 on the body and brain. It also suggests that long-term studies should begin immediately to assess just how severe the effects could be. 👨‍⚕️👩‍⚕️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'UNILAD TECH Jeff Bezos makes a last-minute plea and offers NASA $2 billion to pick Blue Origin's lunar lander over SpaceX'.

node.text: In a letter to NASA administrator Bill Nelson, Bezos said he’d permanently waive up to $2 billion in contract payments for the first two years if NASA adds Blue Origin’s Blue Moon lunar lander to a key phase of the agency’s Human Landing System program 🚀💰

node.text: A 1972 model by MIT researchers predicted a societal collapse by around 2040 and we're bang on track apparently 👀😬

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on July 26, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'UNILAD TECH A new flying jet motorcycle just completeda prototype test flight'.

node.text: The tests showed it could hover, turn, move in various directions and right itself after being knocked over. All are incredibly difficult feats when working with four jet engines! 💪
